Package at.htl.timetableGenerator.factory

package at.htl.timetableGenerator.factory
This package provides factories for common classes used in the timetable generator application. Factories are classes that provide methods for creating objects of other classes. They are used to encapsulate the logic for creating objects, making the code more modular and easier to maintain.
